eplyTime":"2018-05-29T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab8366a7f5954fd7bdd5ea3dda5c88f7ec2504e","tid":683153,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"d844558766e6f1f107a587e3534935f299b90fe7","tid":683153,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab8366a7f5954fd7bdd5ea3dda5c88f7ec2504e","tid":683153,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"你個名點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4d9578636e841c256cb48f3b7ce006788a9cb1","tid":683153,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"c81409c10fb8329d7d38955633c043bf8ea04957","tid":683153,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0a529181efd98782203ba2d5c340a7e8d4b09d","tid":683153,"uid":23433,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"36bce5f10b7682a0e07874b074e0d4e3757b4780","tid":683153,"uid":86236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"生活"},{"pid":"532c2129df7aa0325bf1e88e5397f718bcc2a1df","tid":683153,"uid":117947,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"唔番工